WEBVTT

00:01:24.610 --> 00:01:26.440
BLEACH: THOUSAND-YEAR BLOOD WAR

00:02:16.120 --> 00:02:17.670
Uryu Ishida.

00:02:19.120 --> 00:02:22.500
You look like you've got
a lot on your mind.

00:02:26.330 --> 00:02:27.670
You're the one...

00:02:28.130 --> 00:02:31.010
...who looks like you've
got a lot on your mind.

00:02:31.960 --> 00:02:33.720
Have you forgotten?

00:02:33.720 --> 00:02:36.510
While His Majesty sleeps,

00:02:36.510 --> 00:02:39.100
His Majesty's power and my power
can be switched.

00:02:42.180 --> 00:02:44.640
Being able to see the future...

00:02:44.640 --> 00:02:47.110
...is a very troubling thing.

00:02:47.110 --> 00:02:50.110
Isn't that right, Uryu Ishida?

00:02:52.150 --> 00:02:55.200
Did you foresee my betrayal?

00:02:55.740 --> 00:02:58.200
Why would you say that?

00:02:58.200 --> 00:03:00.780
I haven't said anything yet.

00:03:01.660 --> 00:03:05.050
It seems like you unintentionally
spoke your mind

00:03:05.050 --> 00:03:07.880
because you know you can't hide
from His Majesty's power.

00:03:07.880 --> 00:03:09.210
I'm just looking for a fight.

00:03:10.130 --> 00:03:12.210
Looking for a fight, huh?

00:03:23.350 --> 00:03:26.600
Finally, we're arriving
at the enemy's base.

00:03:27.150 --> 00:03:28.600
Let's go!

00:03:28.940 --> 00:03:29.680
Yes!

00:03:33.650 --> 00:03:34.860
What's the matter?

00:03:51.500 --> 00:03:55.010
He jumped really far.

00:03:56.190 --> 00:03:59.930
Intruders! You've done well
making it this far!

00:04:00.220 --> 00:04:02.560
It's not like we came to you.

00:04:02.560 --> 00:04:04.220
You came jumping at us.

00:04:04.220 --> 00:04:06.680
But this is as far as you'll get.

00:04:06.680 --> 00:04:11.190
If you wish to go any further,
you will have to get past me!

00:04:11.190 --> 00:04:13.230
He isn't listening at all.

00:04:13.230 --> 00:04:14.780
What's with this guy?

00:04:15.050 --> 00:04:17.400
We don't have time
for your nonsense.

00:04:17.400 --> 00:04:18.070
Move!

00:04:21.660 --> 00:04:23.910
Well, if he says so...

00:04:24.330 --> 00:04:26.620
Then I'll just have
to take him down quickly!

00:04:27.330 --> 00:04:28.160
Renji!

00:04:28.160 --> 00:04:29.250
Abarai!

00:04:30.580 --> 00:04:33.630
So you're fine, Renji.

00:04:34.880 --> 00:04:36.010
Yeah.

00:04:46.890 --> 00:04:48.430
Hey, he is over there!

00:04:49.690 --> 00:04:52.400
Red monkey! Are you still alive? Hey!

00:04:55.440 --> 00:04:58.610
His chest is completely pierced through.

00:04:58.610 --> 00:05:01.320
And the wound is very clean.

00:05:01.320 --> 00:05:03.160
It should not be a problem then.

00:05:03.490 --> 00:05:06.040
Hachigen, wake him up.

00:05:06.350 --> 00:05:07.540
Okay.

00:05:07.540 --> 00:05:08.690
Wake him up...

00:05:15.710 --> 00:05:17.260
So you and Ishida...

00:05:19.380 --> 00:05:21.010
Can we leave him to you?

00:05:21.550 --> 00:05:23.110
That was my plan.

00:05:26.970 --> 00:05:28.180
No way!

00:05:29.890 --> 00:05:31.310
Darn!

00:05:36.230 --> 00:05:39.820
Who said this was a one-on-one battle?

00:05:40.170 --> 00:05:45.030
Even a miracle wouldn't be able to save you
in a one-on-one battle with me!

00:05:45.030 --> 00:05:46.830
Come at me, all of you!

00:05:47.740 --> 00:05:49.370
You sound really sure of yourself.

00:05:52.620 --> 00:05:56.210
Right after one fight,
there is another one.

00:05:56.920 --> 00:06:00.510
Battles never end, do they?

00:06:02.340 --> 00:06:08.390
Let's take this moment to learn about
the Schutzstaffel before the next battle.

00:06:09.640 --> 00:06:12.670
Lille is the captain of the Schutzstaffel.

00:06:13.100 --> 00:06:16.770
Lille was the first Quincy that
His Majesty gave a Schrift to.

00:06:16.770 --> 00:06:18.950
His status is unshakable.

00:06:19.470 --> 00:06:20.400
But...

00:06:20.400 --> 00:06:26.870
Pernida and Gerard are Quincies
who haven't been granted power by His Majesty.

00:06:27.240 --> 00:06:29.200
Among the Sternritters,

00:06:29.580 --> 00:06:33.370
they are the only two who got Schrifts

00:06:33.370 --> 00:06:36.260
from His Majesty based on
their original powers.

00:06:36.750 --> 00:06:41.600
As a result, there have always been
strange rumors about who they really are.

00:06:41.600 --> 00:06:42.590
It is said that

00:06:43.170 --> 00:06:47.730
Pernida is actually
"the left arm of the Soul King."

00:06:47.730 --> 00:06:51.090
While Gerard is "the Soul King's heart."

00:06:53.200 --> 00:06:57.440
How come rumors say they are related
to the Soul King when they are Quincies?

00:06:57.440 --> 00:06:59.070
It makes you curious, right?

00:06:59.610 --> 00:07:00.570
But...

00:07:01.070 --> 00:07:03.320
He no longer hears me.

00:07:04.070 --> 00:07:05.200
Kurosaki!

00:07:07.450 --> 00:07:09.950
S-Stay back...

00:07:11.040 --> 00:07:14.080
Brazo Derecho Del Gigante!

00:07:22.920 --> 00:07:25.220
What's going on?

00:07:26.010 --> 00:07:26.970
I can't stand...

00:07:27.510 --> 00:07:30.470
You can't stand, right?

00:07:31.220 --> 00:07:32.970
Gift Bad.

00:07:33.680 --> 00:07:37.770
Entering this pool will not kill you,

00:07:37.770 --> 00:07:41.510
but it will weaken your defenses
against the substance I selected.

00:07:42.440 --> 00:07:45.490
The substance I've chosen
this time is Reishi.

00:07:46.070 --> 00:07:47.490
Reishi?

00:07:47.830 --> 00:07:52.820
You are currently in the Wahrwelt,
where the Reishi concentration is very high,

00:07:52.820 --> 00:07:55.370
and you are exhibiting symptoms
of Reishi poisoning.

00:07:56.000 --> 00:07:59.380
Reishi poisoning?

00:07:59.730 --> 00:08:04.380
Yeah, my power is called
The Deathdealing.

00:08:04.880 --> 00:08:09.260
I can manipulate the lethal dose of
a selected substance to kill my enemies.

00:08:09.260 --> 00:08:15.430
For that, I must consume a large amount
of the selected substance.

00:08:15.430 --> 00:08:19.020
If it's blood, I need to drink a lot of it.

00:08:19.350 --> 00:08:23.770
But I am so full from
drinking too much today.

00:08:24.650 --> 00:08:29.910
So before I'm hungry,
I'll have you just wait here patiently.

00:08:31.530 --> 00:08:34.410
Another person who likes
to talk nonsense.

00:08:34.790 --> 00:08:38.660
If the opponent can't move,
why not just strangle them?

00:08:39.870 --> 00:08:42.420
Are you being serious?

00:08:42.420 --> 00:08:45.090
Well, Bambi also said
something similar back then.

00:08:45.090 --> 00:08:49.470
It pissed me off back then,
and it pisses me off now.

00:08:49.850 --> 00:08:53.030
Could you be a bit...

00:08:53.030 --> 00:08:54.140
...more insensitive?!

00:09:00.100 --> 00:09:02.400
What do you mean
by being insensitive?

00:09:02.400 --> 00:09:04.730
Does that mean taking somebody lightly?

00:09:05.110 --> 00:09:06.360
Not at all.

00:09:06.360 --> 00:09:09.450
It means defeating an enemy
in one's own style.

00:09:10.530 --> 00:09:14.200
Manipulating lethal doses
is my consistent style.

00:09:14.700 --> 00:09:20.460
And strangling people is more suited
to women like you and Bambi.

00:09:22.290 --> 00:09:23.670
I see.

00:09:28.800 --> 00:09:32.130
I have no idea who this person Bambi is,

00:09:33.590 --> 00:09:37.720
but the point you're trying to make is
that's how the beautiful ladies do things.

00:09:38.040 --> 00:09:41.560
Well, you and Bambi
are indeed both beautiful.

00:09:41.560 --> 00:09:44.230
But a woman's value isn't in her look.

00:09:46.070 --> 00:09:47.940
It's whether she's stylish or not!

00:09:55.320 --> 00:09:59.200
Sorry, you're quite an interesting guy.

00:09:59.910 --> 00:10:02.500
But we're in a hurry.

00:10:08.000 --> 00:10:09.670
I need to pass through by force.

00:10:15.390 --> 00:10:17.970
Shunko! Raijin Senkei!

00:10:28.020 --> 00:10:29.900
You are really underestimating us.

00:10:29.900 --> 00:10:34.910
There are captains and lieutenants of
Thirteen Court Guard Squads here.

00:10:35.490 --> 00:10:38.660
There's no way you could
take us down by yourself.

00:10:41.450 --> 00:10:43.470
I can't win?

00:10:44.310 --> 00:10:46.170
Do you think so?

00:10:47.460 --> 00:10:53.800
Then if I do defeat you all,
it would be a miracle!

00:10:54.150 --> 00:10:58.350
Do you know when miracles happen?

00:10:58.350 --> 00:11:04.810
If a miracle occurs in a meaningless moment,
people will not recognize it as a miracle.

00:11:05.230 --> 00:11:07.350
"You are so lucky!"

00:11:07.350 --> 00:11:09.820
"Life has some crazy things going on."

00:11:09.820 --> 00:11:12.570
That is all they will probably think.

00:11:13.280 --> 00:11:15.190
What are you talking about?

00:11:15.190 --> 00:11:18.700
As expected of the captains and lieutenants
of the Thirteen Court Guard Squads.

00:11:19.200 --> 00:11:22.470
You've wounded me to this extent.

00:11:23.580 --> 00:11:24.660
A miracle...

00:11:24.660 --> 00:11:27.420
...is a miracle because it occurs in a crisis!

00:11:29.960 --> 00:11:30.840
Captain?

00:11:31.500 --> 00:11:32.800
I'm finishing him off.

00:11:36.840 --> 00:11:40.680
Did we really need to go this far?

00:11:40.680 --> 00:11:45.060
Idiot, he was clearly still hiding
some trump card up his sleeve.

00:11:45.060 --> 00:11:46.980
Besides, according to what he said,

00:11:46.980 --> 00:11:51.190
it's a trump card that can reverse
the entire situation in a single attack.

00:11:51.730 --> 00:11:54.780
If we don't go this far,
we have no idea what might happen.

00:11:55.570 --> 00:11:58.200
Right, Captain Kuchiki?

00:12:05.160 --> 00:12:07.710
We can't be too sure, right?

00:12:07.710 --> 00:12:09.210
How frightening.

00:12:09.590 --> 00:12:10.430
Let's go.

00:12:24.010 --> 00:12:25.430
This shaking...

00:12:35.610 --> 00:12:39.240
Heal quickly, then head to Tenshukaku.

00:12:39.240 --> 00:12:41.650
We must defeat Yhwach as soon as possible.

00:12:41.650 --> 00:12:43.330
Otherwise, this world will be doomed.

00:12:44.370 --> 00:12:45.450
Okay.

00:12:52.880 --> 00:12:55.710
Karin, there was an earthquake!

00:12:55.710 --> 00:12:58.340
Yeah, the juice has spilled.

00:12:59.260 --> 00:13:02.720
Sorry, I was afraid
you would be in danger.

00:13:02.720 --> 00:13:05.560
Don't worry,
the game machine was not wet.

00:13:05.850 --> 00:13:07.520
I'm sorry.

00:13:07.520 --> 00:13:09.440
I said don't worry.

00:13:10.640 --> 00:13:12.190
It's still shaking.

00:13:36.000 --> 00:13:39.010
GERARD VALKYRIE

00:13:39.010 --> 00:13:41.970
SAKIMUNE SHIHOIN YUUSHIRO

00:13:56.190 --> 00:13:57.360
Miss Yoruichi.

00:13:58.110 --> 00:14:00.210
You have recovered rapidly.

00:14:01.280 --> 00:14:02.310
You guys go ahead.

00:14:02.310 --> 00:14:04.990
After making sure that guy is dead,
I'll catch up with you.

00:14:05.330 --> 00:14:06.150
Understood.

00:14:06.720 --> 00:14:09.080
Be careful, Miss Yoruichi.

00:14:09.450 --> 00:14:11.580
Who do you think you're talking to?

00:14:11.580 --> 00:14:13.710
There's no way I'll lose.

00:14:16.840 --> 00:14:18.840
Inoue, Chad.

00:14:18.840 --> 00:14:19.730
Yeah.

00:14:24.680 --> 00:14:26.930
They're getting through...

00:14:26.930 --> 00:14:29.690
His Majesty is going to scold me.

00:14:30.810 --> 00:14:33.940
Don't worry, you won't be scolded.

00:14:33.940 --> 00:14:36.860
Because I will defeat you and Yhwach.

00:14:37.250 --> 00:14:40.860
With that "Ray Something"
attack you used earlier?

00:14:41.280 --> 00:14:44.150
Well, that's a headache.

00:14:44.150 --> 00:14:46.020
It's Raijin Senkei!

00:14:48.700 --> 00:14:50.490
Not "Ray Something"!

00:14:50.490 --> 00:14:52.080
It's Raijin Senkei!

00:14:52.080 --> 00:14:55.330
If you're going to insult my sister,
you'll have to deal with me!

00:14:55.710 --> 00:14:57.040
Sister?

00:14:57.040 --> 00:14:59.250
Why are you here?

00:14:59.800 --> 00:15:01.590
I've come to help you!

00:15:03.400 --> 00:15:06.390
Oh, help me, huh?

00:15:06.390 --> 00:15:08.850
You want to help me?

00:15:08.850 --> 00:15:10.060
Yes!

00:15:10.060 --> 00:15:11.970
Yushiro...

00:15:11.970 --> 00:15:16.440
In the short time I've been away,
it looks like you've gotten a little stronger.

00:15:16.760 --> 00:15:17.860
Yes!

00:15:19.270 --> 00:15:22.860
I'm so happy you noticed!

00:15:22.860 --> 00:15:27.530
I-I've gotten stronger!

00:15:27.910 --> 00:15:33.500
That's right. He's too stupid
to recognize sarcasm...

00:15:33.500 --> 00:15:35.120
Okay. Okay.

00:15:35.500 --> 00:15:37.790
Let's end this touching story here.

00:15:37.790 --> 00:15:39.750
Wanna fight with me, young lady?

00:15:40.150 --> 00:15:41.040
I...

00:15:42.250 --> 00:15:44.090
I'm a boy!

00:15:44.400 --> 00:15:47.180
Really? Well, sorry then.

00:15:59.120 --> 00:16:00.650
W-Wait a minute...

00:16:00.650 --> 00:16:03.110
Holy crap! You're so strong!

00:16:03.110 --> 00:16:04.190
Of course I am!

00:16:04.570 --> 00:16:07.150
I am the 23rd head of the Shihoin family,

00:16:07.150 --> 00:16:09.620
Shihoin Yuushiro Sakimune.

00:16:09.620 --> 00:16:12.490
There's no way I'd lose to a mere Quincy!

00:16:12.490 --> 00:16:13.580
Shunko!

00:16:13.870 --> 00:16:15.830
Bakuen Muso!

00:16:27.720 --> 00:16:30.550
What is this? Is this a foot?

00:16:44.570 --> 00:16:47.740
W-What is that monster?!

00:16:56.040 --> 00:17:01.000
My name is Gerard Valkyrie!

00:17:03.520 --> 00:17:08.040
My Schrift is "M"! The Miracle Gerard!

00:17:10.550 --> 00:17:16.520
My power is to turn the damage I've taken
and convert it into the "God Size."

00:17:17.180 --> 00:17:18.930
I'll say this just once more.

00:17:19.430 --> 00:17:23.110
As expected of the captains and lieutenants
of the Thirteen Court Guard Squads.

00:17:23.110 --> 00:17:26.610
You've wounded me to this extent.

00:17:28.820 --> 00:17:32.360
This is the first time
I've become this massive...

00:17:32.910 --> 00:17:34.530
...from an exchange!

00:17:36.740 --> 00:17:37.370
Momo!

00:17:38.250 --> 00:17:40.370
Captain, watch your back!

00:17:43.130 --> 00:17:44.880
Momo, I will leave it to you.

00:17:44.880 --> 00:17:45.590
Yes!

00:17:53.470 --> 00:17:54.390
Bloom.

00:17:54.970 --> 00:17:56.470
Tobiume!

00:17:57.640 --> 00:17:59.390
Hado 91.

00:18:01.440 --> 00:18:03.520
Senju Koten Taiho.

00:18:06.980 --> 00:18:08.780
That hurts!

00:18:14.700 --> 00:18:15.820
We did it!

00:18:15.820 --> 00:18:17.700
It worked!

00:18:19.580 --> 00:18:20.330
Hinamori!

00:18:20.330 --> 00:18:21.410
Captain Hirako!

00:18:29.170 --> 00:18:31.340
Jakuho Raikoben!

00:18:31.970 --> 00:18:33.050
Captain!

00:18:33.050 --> 00:18:33.970
Brother!

00:18:35.970 --> 00:18:38.010
Let's go, Rukia!

00:18:38.010 --> 00:18:38.970
Okay!

00:18:53.860 --> 00:18:56.200
Powerless! Utterly powerless!

00:18:56.780 --> 00:18:59.620
Being powerless is really terrifying!

00:19:00.370 --> 00:19:02.450
But do not lament.

00:19:03.870 --> 00:19:07.460
No matter how much you lament,

00:19:08.250 --> 00:19:10.670
no miracle will be coming for you!

00:19:13.510 --> 00:19:14.800
Oh, my.

00:19:15.670 --> 00:19:19.140
Not only did you steal my thunder,
but you did it in such a fancy way.

00:19:20.260 --> 00:19:22.810
S-Sorry, Sis.

00:19:24.560 --> 00:19:25.590
Although...

00:19:26.140 --> 00:19:30.570
Maybe I should commend you
for mastering the Shunko

00:19:30.920 --> 00:19:32.730
that I just taught you.

00:19:34.360 --> 00:19:38.410
What? You just learned it
and already mastered it to this extent?

00:19:39.660 --> 00:19:42.740
Hey, now. What's with that look?

00:19:42.740 --> 00:19:44.330
I told you, didn't I?

00:19:44.330 --> 00:19:50.210
I can control the lethal dose
of a substance through massive intake.

00:19:52.130 --> 00:19:56.170
I truly do thank you for bringing upon me
a near-fatal amount of Spiritual Pressure.

00:19:56.170 --> 00:20:00.050
Now, your Spiritual Pressure
will no longer be able to kill me.

00:20:00.510 --> 00:20:03.430
Are your wounds healing?

00:20:03.770 --> 00:20:05.520
Isn't that obvious?

00:20:05.520 --> 00:20:10.190
By raising the lethal dosage,
I've become immune to your attacks.

00:20:11.690 --> 00:20:14.440
I don't think you have
the time to be shocked.

00:20:14.850 --> 00:20:18.200
If you don't hurry,
forget about killing me,

00:20:18.200 --> 00:20:21.200
you will not even be able to
leave a scratch on me.

00:20:22.530 --> 00:20:23.410
Shunko!

00:20:26.580 --> 00:20:27.910
Wait, Yushiro!

00:20:29.920 --> 00:20:32.880
You don't get it, do you?

00:20:32.880 --> 00:20:34.920
I've already taken that earlier.

00:20:38.760 --> 00:20:41.720
So I've already acquired immunity to it.

00:20:42.680 --> 00:20:43.560
Yushiro!

00:20:45.180 --> 00:20:46.310
It's too late.

00:20:47.890 --> 00:20:51.860
It took you so long to finally
realize my true power.

00:20:54.320 --> 00:20:56.310
This is lethal...

00:20:56.850 --> 00:20:59.020
...Yoruichi Shihoin.

00:21:01.010 --> 00:21:04.080
That is what someone who can't see
the scales would say.

00:21:04.080 --> 00:21:05.540
Uryu Ishida.

00:21:06.700 --> 00:21:08.290
What do you mean?

00:21:09.210 --> 00:21:12.290
The time has come to reveal
the truth and lies.

00:21:13.420 --> 00:21:17.010
If you're here as a successor,

00:21:17.890 --> 00:21:19.670
then prove it to me.

00:21:20.050 --> 00:21:23.800
Prove you're not a traitor!

00:21:26.140 --> 00:21:28.020
Wait, Haschwalth!

00:21:33.690 --> 00:21:34.440
BLEACH EPISODE 39

00:21:34.900 --> 00:21:36.020
Ishida.

00:21:38.490 --> 00:21:39.990
Kurosaki.

00:21:40.570 --> 00:21:41.950
THE VISIBLE ANSWER

00:23:18.340 --> 00:23:20.170
I knew you would be here.

00:23:22.090 --> 00:23:23.550
What's the matter?

00:23:24.590 --> 00:23:26.580
It seems like it is almost time.

00:23:29.010 --> 00:23:30.430
You're going, aren't you?

00:23:36.810 --> 00:23:39.010
If words possessed a physical form,

00:23:40.070 --> 00:23:44.290
you would be unable to perceive it
while standing in the darkness.

00:23:46.110 --> 00:23:49.950
BLEACH EPISODE 40: MY LAST WORDS

